Thank you for coming.

89
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:30,520
I'm sorry to drag you all
the way out here with me.

90
00:05:30,520 --> 00:05:32,840
You don't need to
apologize for anything.

91
00:05:32,840 --> 00:05:35,720
I'm the one who recommended
spa therapy, remember?

92
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:38,720
If anybody could use some
serious R&R, it's you.

93
00:05:38,720 --> 00:05:42,680
And besides, this isn't exactly
torture for me, you know.

94
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:45,520
True.

95
00:05:45,520 --> 00:05:47,880
Throw your worries away!

96
00:05:47,880 --> 00:05:48,760
Wow.

97
00:05:48,760 --> 00:05:51,520
This looks more like a
royal palace than a hotel.

98
00:05:51,520 --> 00:05:54,400
I knew it'd be nice since
it was prize from a game show,

99
00:05:54,400 --> 00:05:56,720
but this is amazing.

100
