[YAWNING]

101
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:00,240
So what's with the yawning?

102
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:01,680
Not impressive enough for you?

103
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:03,480
Hey, sorry I'm not
doing cartwheels.

104
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:05,640
I just can't seem to
shake this fatigue.

105
00:06:05,640 --> 00:06:07,440
I think I'm exhausted
from dealing with

106
00:06:07,440 --> 00:06:09,080
your irritable moods every day.

107
00:06:09,080 --> 00:06:11,280
Look, it's your fault
that I'm irritable.

108
00:06:11,280 --> 00:06:12,560
Do you know how
exhausting it is‐‐

109
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:13,360
Whatever.

110
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:15,280
You, me, I'd just like to
try and relax for a change,

111
00:06:15,280 --> 00:06:16,080
all right?

112
00:06:16,080 --> 00:06:18,040
So what are we waiting for?

113
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:18,920
I can't believe this.

114
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:20,640
Like I am irritable.

115
00:06:20,640 --> 00:06:24,200
What idiot thought it
would be fun to invite him?

116
00:06:24,200 --> 00:06:26,240
Should we tell her it
was her father's idea?

117
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:33,440
OK, Kazuma, Ren, looks
like that's your room.

118
00:06:33,440 --> 00:06:35,600
And we're right across the hall.

119
00:06:35,600 --> 00:06:36,520
So now what?

120
00:06:36,520 --> 00:06:37,680
What should we do first?

121
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:39,080
I say we hit the hotsprings.

122
00:06:39,080 --> 00:06:39,840
Oh wait.

123
00:06:39,840 --> 00:06:40,680
Check this out.

124
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:41,800
It says they have a spa.

125
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:42,720
Why don't we do that?

126
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:44,240
Yeah, that's even better.

127
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:45,120
REN: What do you think?

128
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:46,720
Do you wanna head
down there too?

129
00:06:46,720 --> 00:06:48,160
KAZUMA: Nah, you go ahead.

130
00:06:48,160 --> 00:06:51,240
I just wanna relax in the
outdoor hot tub for a while.

131
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:52,240
REN: Oh, OK.

132
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:54,120
I guess you are
pretty tired, huh?

133
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:55,160
Well, get some good rest.

134
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:01,920
Whoa.

135
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:04,680
Look at the size of this place.

136
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:07,400
Yeah, there's a lot to do,
but if we get started now,

137
00:07:07,400 --> 00:07:09,200
I think we could see it all.

138
00:07:09,200 --> 00:07:10,880
Mhm.

139
00:07:10,880 --> 00:07:11,680
Wow.

140
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:14,240
There can't be anything
better than a cypress bath.

141
00:07:14,240 --> 00:07:16,000
That's the truth.

142
00:07:16,000 --> 00:07:19,040
Yeah, I couldn't agree more.

143
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:19,800
Oh wow.

144
00:07:19,800 --> 00:07:22,560
There can't be anything
better than a jacuzzi.

145
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:24,080
